      <title>韩国外汇储备因干预创 19 个月来最大单月跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/south-korea-fx-reserves-log-biggest-monthly-drop-19-months-intervention-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当局干预货币市场以遏制韩元货币贬值，韩国 4 月份外汇储备跌幅为 19 个月来最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/south-korea-fx-reserves-log-biggest-monthly-drop-19-months-intervention-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 21:06:47 GMT</pubDate>
